prompts.frontCover: Greeting card front cover, a humorous and beautiful botanical scene featuring cartoon-illustrated versions of Lao Lao and Jordan from the reference photo. The setting is a lush, oversized garden where everything is comically out of scale. Lao Lao sits triumphantly on a giant, detailed mushroom cap, holding a comically small birthday cake with one lit candle. She has a wide, happy grin, and wears her light blue sweatshirt and glasses. Jordan, wearing his tan hoodie, is peeking out playfully from behind a massive, stylized fern frond next to the mushroom, his expression one of loving amusement as he looks at Lao Lao. The background is a dense tapestry of whimsical botanical elements: oversized flowers, curling vines, and colorful foliage in soft, natural watercolor tones. The overall style is flat 2D illustration with clean lines and a vibrant yet gentle color palette. Centered in the upper middle area, the text "Happy Birthday Lao Lao!" is written in a beautiful, flowing, and easily readable handwritten cursive script.
